## Notes

- Screens in this packet are **not** an HSIP application. They are a
  cycle-readiness diagnostic the lead agency uses to focus effort on
  candidates that can clear FHWA HSIP eligibility before the full
  application package is assembled.
- Every screen in this packet is mirrored as an `hsip_project_screen`
  fact_block (plus one `hsip_portfolio_summary`) appended to this run's
  `fact_blocks.jsonl`, so subsequent narrative and chat turns remain
  subject to the ClawModeler citation contract.

